Kent.The Outlet Collection Seattle:
The Outlet Collection Seattle, formerly SuperMall of the Great Northwest, is an outlet mall in Auburn, Washington. It is anchored by Bed Bath & Beyond, Burlington Coat Factory, Dave & Buster's, Nordstrom Rack, Sam's Club, Old Navy, and LA Fitness.


== History ==
The Outlet Collection Seattle originally opened in 1995 under the name "Supermall of the Great Northwest".
